---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About Us | Bobo Analytics">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="glow-bg"></div>
    <h1>About <span class="gradient-text">Bobo Analytics</span></h1>
    <p class="lead">We are on a mission to bring advanced AI analytics to every business, regardless of size or industry.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="story-grid">
      <div class="story-content">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Founded in 2026, Bobo Analytics started with a simple observation: while large corporations were leveraging AI to optimize their operations, small and medium-sized businesses were being left behind. The data divide was widening.</p>
        <p>We built Bobo to bridge that gap. By democratizing access to cutting-edge predictive analytics and inventory management, we level the playing field for ambitious businesses everywhere.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vision-content">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <div class="vision-card">
          <div class="icon">🌍</div>
          <p>To become the world's most intuitive and powerful analytics platform, empowering business owners with the insights they need to thrive in a data-driven world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values-section">
    <h2>Core Values</h2>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">💡</div>
        <h3>Innovation</h3>
        <p>We constantly push the boundaries of what AI can do for retail, healthcare, and <strong>artisanal home-based bakery</strong> operations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">🤝</div>
        <h3>Partnership</h3>
        <p>Your success is our success. We treat every client as a long-term partner.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">🔒</div>
        <h3>Trust & Security</h3>
        <p>Your data is sacred. We employ military-grade encryption to ensure complete privacy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about-hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 24px 80px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .glow-bg {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 600px;
      height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #a855f7 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .story-section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto 100px;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .story-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .story-content h2, .vision-content h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: white;
    }

    .story-content p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .vision-card {
      background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .vision-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 4px;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #6366f1, #a855f7);
    }

    .vision-card .icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .vision-card p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .values-section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto 100px;
      padding: 0 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .values-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .values-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .value-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .value-card:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    }

    .icon-circle {
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
    }

    .value-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .value-card p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .story-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
